# Snorty

[Snort](https://www.snort.org/) in Docker hosted on [Ubuntu 20.04](https://ubuntu.com/)


The Snort Version 2.9.18.1 | DAQ Version 2.0.7 | Community Rules added

# Build image locally

```
 $ sudo docker build -t snorty .
```
# Docker Usage
You may need to run as `sudo`
Attach the snort in container to have full access to the network

```
$ docker run -it --rm --net=host linton/docker-snort /bin/bash
```
